Fig. 10
). Epistoma and frontoclypeal sutures slightly arcuate. Clypeus (
Fig. 12
) transverse, with two pairs of clypeal setae (
cls 1–2
), anterior margin concave. Labrum (
Fig. 12
) transverse, with three pairs of labral setae (
